    "body": "Right this seems like an unintended ux.\r\nsetting the gas limit is specific to using the builder, i think what solves this is throwing an error when builder settings don't exist, as builder logic requires a set fee recipient on the validator client side ( in addition to the beacon node side) to enable which should resolve this. will look at the fix sometime soon. thanks for reporting.\r\n\r\n*note to self try to find a way where we can do this without really throwing errors...*",
